<p><strong>Ad-hoc</strong> – As and when you need us</p>
<p>Do you simply want professional and accurate HR advice? Need a hand to implement new policies? Or have a difficult employee relation issue? Then our ad-hoc service is just what you’re looking for. You can pick up the phone and talk to us, or send as an e-mail and our HR professionals will be happy to help.</p>
<p>You’re not tied into a contract; we’re simply there for you when you need us. You have access to advice, implementation, documentation and HR project work tailored to your needs.</p>
<p>To see the full range of services that we provide please visit www.edenhrconsuting.com or contact us for a free no obligation quotation and to talk us through your requirements.</p></td>
